Cinnamal is a Linux desktop which provides advanced innovative features and a power user experience.

The desktop layout is similar to Cinnamon with enhanced menu and without a desktop
It is forked from Cinnamon.
It will maintain full compatiblity with Cinnamon.
The emphasis is put on making users feel at home and providing them with an easy to use and comfortable desktop experience.

